    subtitle='The HKUST Media Intelligence Research Center is a leading hub for media innovation in Asia, dedicated to pioneering research, advancing cutting-edge technologies, and shaping the future of global media. Inspired by the vision of becoming the "Eastern MIT," we bring together world-class talent, industry partnerships, and academic excellence to drive breakthroughs that connect technology, culture, and society.'
